# 03 - Code Review
# Analyze code files and provide feedback

NAME code-review
INPUT path
INPUT language DEFAULT "auto-detect"

GOAL scan "Use glob and read tools to find and read source files in $path. Identify the $language if auto-detect."
GOAL review "Review the code for: bugs, security issues, performance problems, and style inconsistencies."
GOAL suggest "Provide specific, actionable improvements with code examples where helpful. Save the review to code-review-output.md."

RUN review_flow USING scan, review, suggest
